OL,4,CJJ Chalmers: Meeting the pilot who flew
OL,5,Cme home injured from Afghanistan
OL,6, BBC presenter JJ Chalmers has said he
OL,7, "burst into tears" when he realised the
OL,8, pilot flying him to the Tokyo
OL,9, Paralympics was the same man who flew
OL,10, him home injured from Afghanistan.
OL,12,FChalmers was injured in a bomb blast
OL,13,Fwhile serving as a Royal Marine
OL,14,FCommando in Afghanistan in 2011.
OL,16,FWhile on the plane to Tokyo to cover
OL,17,Fthe Paralympics for BBC Radio 5 Live,
OL,18,Fan air stewardess pulled him aside and
OL,19,Fsaid the pilot had recognised his name.
OL,21,FChalmers said he felt "overwhelmed".
